      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Taiwanese-style basil chicken thigh stir-fry</strong> with the <strong>sticky rice </strong>to the side</p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into a small bowl and turn out</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
